text: Victor Asirvatham was a sprinter from Malaysia. Victor competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics and the 1968 Summer Olympics. He was born on 25 September 1940 and died on 11 May 2021.Victor Asirvatham == References == Category:1940 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Olympians for Malaysia Category:Sprinters
